definitions.definition: A material of short fiber and inferior quality obtained by deviling woollen rags or the remnants of woollen goods, specifically those of felted, milled, or hard-spun woollen cloth, as distinguished from shoddy , or the deviled product of loose-textured woollen goods or worsted .
